        "localization": {
          "name": "Modular Shot",
          "description": "1250% damage to 2 enemies. Unlocked each time an ally on the battlefield is defeated by an attack while this unit is on the battlefield. If that ally was:\n- Water, this attack grants hit targets Sleep (Forced) for 200TU.\n- Fire, this attack grants all allies the Burn status effect.\n- Storm, this attack grants hit targets Stun for 200TU.\n- Earth, this attack grants hit targets Cursed Sleep for 200TU (blocked by Burn).\n- Light, this attack heals all allies for 100% of max HP and Purifies them.\n- Dark, this attack grants hit targets Mega Poison for 200TU.\nSuccessfully applied Status Effects will overwrite existing status effects on affected units.\n\nThis skill is locked again after each use or if the user leaves the battlefield. The Elemental effect will be determined at the time this skill unlocks. When multiple allies are defeated at the same time, only one Element will be considered.",
          "selected": "1250% damage, grants Elemental effect\n(Will overwrite other status effects)"
        }
